languages.text: "Я осмотрел{mf||а} тела нападавших, что были убиты сегодня. Все они были высокофункциональными сервиторами. Такие есть в распоряжении лишь близких Адептус Механикус семьях, не так ли?"

traits.locale_text: "Я осмотрел{mf||а} тела нападавших, что были убиты сегодня. Все они были высокофункциональными сервиторами. Такие есть в распоряжении лишь близких Адептус Механикус семьях, не так ли?"

languages.text: "I have examined the bodies of the assailants that were killed today. All of them were high-functioning servitors. Such servitors are only employed by families close to the Adeptus Mechanicus, isn't that so?"

languages.text: 「今日殺された襲撃者の死体を調べてきた。襲撃者の全員が、高機能サーヴィターだった。たしか、こうしたサーヴィターは帝国技術局に近しい家しか雇えないものだ」

languages.text: “我调查了那些刺客的尸体，他们都是高智能型机仆。如果我没记错的话，只有与机械修会关系密切的家族才能雇佣到这样的杀手，是这样吧？”
languages.original_text: "I have examined the bodies of the assailants that were killed today. All of them were high-functioning servitors. Such servitors are only employed by families close to the Adeptus Mechanicus, isn't that so?"

traits.locale_text: “我调查了那些刺客的尸体，他们都是高智能型奴工。如果我没记错的话，只有与机械修会关系密切的家族才能雇佣到这样的杀手。”

languages.text: « J'ai examiné les corps des assaillants tués un peu plus tôt. Ils étaient tous des servitors ultra-performants. De ceux qui sont d'ordinaire employés par les familles proches de l'Adeptus Mechanicus, si je ne m'abuse. »
languages.original_text: "I have examined the bodies of the assailants that were killed today. All of them were high-functioning servitors. Such servitors are only employed by families close to the Adeptus Mechanicus, isn't that so?"

languages.text: «He inspeccionado los cadáveres de los asaltantes abatidos. Todos fueron servidores de alto rendimiento. Solo las familias cercanas al Adeptus Mechanicus contratan ese tipo de servidores, ¿no es así?».
languages.original_text: "I have examined the bodies of the assailants that were killed today. All of them were high-functioning servitors. Such servitors are only employed by families close to the Adeptus Mechanicus, isn't that so?"

languages.text: "Ich habe die Leichen der Attentäter untersucht, die heute getötet wurden. Sie alle waren hochfunktionale Servitoren. Solche Servitoren stehen nur in Diensten der Familien, die dem Adeptus Mechanicus nahestehen, nicht wahr?"
languages.original_text: "I have examined the bodies of the assailants that were killed today. All of them were high-functioning servitors. Such servitors are only employed by families close to the Adeptus Mechanicus, isn't that so?"

traits.locale_text: "Ich habe die Leichen der Attentäter untersucht, die heute getötet worden. Sie alle waren hochfunktionale Servitoren. Solche Servitoren stehen nur in Diensten der Familien, die dem Adeptus Mechanicus nahestehen, wenn mich mein Gedächtnis nicht trügt."

languages.text: "Bugün öldürülen saldırganların cesetlerini inceledim. Hepsi yüksek işlevli hizmetörlerdi. Bu hizmetörler, yalnızca Adeptus Mechanicus'a yakınlığıyla bilinen hanelerce kullanılmıyor mu?"
